spec_data.Name: perl-Number-Bytes-Human
spec_data.Description:
This module is designed to format byte counts to usual readable
format, like '2.0K', '3.1G', '100B'. It was inspired in the -h option of
Unix utilities like du, df and ls for "human-readable" output.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 02:37:53 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Convert byte count to human readable format
